modules.description: Generates spatial transformation functions for user-defined types containing OCADml and CAD-specific types like V3.t, V2.t, and Scad.t. Enables operations such as translation, rotation, and scaling on composite data structures. Used to manipulate 3D modeling data directly within custom type hierarchies.

Generates spatial transformation functions like translate, rotate, and scale for user-defined types containing OCADml and CAD-specific data structures such as V3.t and Scad.t. Supports dimension-specific operations based on the presence of 2D or 3D types and allows custom parameter handling via attributes. Enables direct manipulation of geometric and CAD models within OCaml code.
